            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1283942330,
            "creation_date": 1283880103,
            "body": "<p>Checkout <a href=\"http://netbeans.org/features/java/profiler.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">NetBeans Profiler<\/a>. Suggesting it as no one else has suggested same. This one looks more feature rich.<\/p>\n\n<p>I have used another tool <a href=\"http://www.ej-technologies.com/products/jprofiler/overview.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">\"JProfiler\"<\/a> few times. But its only free for trial.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 3661032,
